=head1 NAME

INSTALL - Apache::AuthzLDAP installation instructions

=head1 DESCRIPTION

How to build, test, configure and install Apache::AuthzLDAP.pm

=head1 PREREQUISITES

=over 3

=back

=head1 Build and install Apache::AuthzLDAP.pm

=over 3

In this current directory run:

  perl Makefile.PL
  make
  make install

=back

=head1 Testing Apache::AuthzLDAP.pm

=over 3

At this time, no regression tests are available.

=back

